
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>🌾 AgroMind AI Agent</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --green-dark:#1a4731;--green:#2d7a4f;--green-mid:#3fa66e;--green-light:#6fcf97;
    --yellow:#f5c542;--orange:#f59342;--red:#e05252;--blue:#3b82f6;
    --bg:#0f1f16;--card:#172b1f;--card2:#1e3829;--border:#2d4a39;
    --text:#e8f5ee;--muted:#7aab8a;--white:#fff;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  /* HEADER */
  header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green-dark),#0d2e1a);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:14px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px}
  .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  .logo-icon{font-size:28px}
  .logo-text h1{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white)}
  .logo-text p{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .header-badges{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .badge{padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.4px}
  .badge-green{background:#1f4d2e;color:var(--green-light);border:1px solid #2d6b40}
  .badge-yellow{background:#3d3010;color:var(--yellow);border:1px solid #5a4515}
  .badge-blue{background:#112240;color:#93c5fd;border:1px solid #1e3a5f}
  /* LAYOUT */
  .layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:260px 1fr 300px;flex:1;min-height:0;height:calc(100vh - 64px)}
  /* SIDEBAR */
  .sidebar{background:var(--card);border-right:1px solid var(--border);padding:16px 0;overflow-y:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
  .sidebar-section{padding:6px 16px;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:8px}
  .nav-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 16px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:0;transition:.15s;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);border-left:3px solid transparent}
  .nav-item:hover{background:var(--card2);color:var(--text)}
  .nav-item.active{background:var(--card2);color:var(--green-light);border-left-color:var(--green-mid)}
  .nav-item .icon{font-size:16px;width:20px;text-align:center}
  .nav-item .alert-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--orange);margin-left:auto;flex-shrink:0}
  /* MAIN */
  .main{overflow-y:auto;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--bg)}
  /* PANEL */
  .panel{display:none;flex-direction:column;height:100%;animation:fadeIn .2s ease}
  .panel.active{display:flex}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  /* TOP BAR */
  .panel-top{padding:18px 24px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--card);flex-shrink:0}
  .panel-top h2{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700}
  .panel-top p{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}
  .btn{padding:7px 14px;border-radius:7px;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--green-mid);color:#fff}
  .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--green)}
  .btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--muted);border:1px solid var(--border)}
  .btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--muted)}
  .btn-danger{background:#3d1515;color:var(--red);border:1px solid #5a2020}
  .btn-row{display:flex;gap:8px}
  /* SCROLL CONTENT */
  .panel-body{padding:20px 24px;overflow-y:auto;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px}
  /* STAT CARDS */
  .stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px}
  .stat-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px}
  .stat-label{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
  .stat-val{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:800;margin:4px 0 2px;line-height:1}
  .stat-sub{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .stat-trend{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600}
  .up{color:#6fcf97}.down{color:var(--red)}.warn{color:var(--yellow)}
  /* SECTION */
  .section{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
  .section-head{padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
  .section-head h3{font-size:.85rem;font-weight:700}
  .section-body{padding:14px 16px}
  /* TABLE */
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.78rem}
  th{text-align:left;padding:7px 10px;color:var(--muted);font-size:.67rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  td{padding:9px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #1c3324}
  tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
  tr:hover td{background:#1c3324}
  /* STATUS PILLS */
  .pill{padding:2px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.67rem;font-weight:700;white-space:nowrap}
  .pill-green{background:#1a3d28;color:#6fcf97}
  .pill-yellow{background:#3d3010;color:#f5c542}
  .pill-red{background:#3d1515;color:#f08080}
  .pill-blue{background:#112240;color:#93c5fd}
  .pill-gray{background:#1e2e23;color:var(--muted)}
  /* PROGRESS */
  .progress-row{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .progress-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.75rem}
  .progress-bar{height:8px;background:#1c3324;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
  .progress-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:.5s}
  .fill-green{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--green-light))}
  .fill-yellow{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#b8870c,#f5c542)}
  .fill-red{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#8b1a1a,#e05252)}
  .fill-blue{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#1e40af,#3b82f6)}
  /* ALERT CARDS */
  .alert-card{border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:8px}
  .alert-card .ico{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
  .alert-card .ac-title{font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:2px}
  .alert-card .ac-body{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
  .alert-card .ac-action{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;border:none;display:inline-block}
  .alert-high{background:#2a1010;border:1px solid #5a2020}
  .alert-med{background:#2a1f05;border:1px solid #5a4010}
  .alert-low{background:#0f2a1f;border:1px solid #1e5a3a}
  .alert-info{background:#0f1f2a;border:1px solid #1e3a5a}
  /* CHAT */
  .chat-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%}
  .chat-messages{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
  .msg{display:flex;gap:10px;animation:fadeIn .2s ease}
  .msg.user{flex-direction:row-reverse}
  .msg-bubble{max-width:82%;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:12px;font-size:.8rem;line-height:1.6}
  .msg.bot .msg-bubble{background:var(--card2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-top-left-radius:3px}
  .msg.user .msg-bubble{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-top-right-radius:3px}
  .msg-avatar{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
  .bot-av{background:var(--green-dark)}
  .user-av{background:#3d4d3d}
  .chat-input-row{padding:12px 14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--card);display:flex;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0}
  .chat-input{flex:1;background:#1c3324;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:9px 13px;color:var(--text);font-size:.82rem;outline:none;resize:none;font-family:inherit}
  .chat-input:focus{border-color:var(--green-mid)}
  .chat-send{background:var(--green-mid);border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 14px;color:#fff;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0}
  .chat-send:hover{background:var(--green)}
  /* SUGGESTION CHIPS */
  .chips{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:8px 14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
  .chip{background:var(--card2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:5px 11px;font-size:.7rem;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);transition:.15s}
  .chip:hover{border-color:var(--green-mid);color:var(--green-light)}
  /* RIGHT PANEL */
  .right-panel{background:var(--card);border-left:1px solid var(--border);overflow-y:auto;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}
  .rp-section{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:14px}
  .rp-title{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px}
  /* WEATHER */
  .weather-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a2a40,#0d3a55);border:1px solid #1e4060;border-radius:10px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .wc-temp{font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff}
  .wc-cond{font-size:.78rem;color:#93c5fd;margin:2px 0 8px}
  .wc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px}
  .wc-item{font-size:.7rem;color:#7ab3cf}
  .wc-item span{color:#e0f0ff;font-weight:600}
  /* COMPLIANCE */
  .compliance-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1c3324;font-size:.75rem}
  .compliance-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .ci-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
  .ci-green{background:var(--green-light)}
  .ci-yellow{background:var(--yellow)}
  .ci-red{background:var(--red)}
  .ci-label{flex:1;color:var(--text)}
  .ci-val{color:var(--muted);font-size:.7rem}
  /* TASKS */
  .task-item{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1c3324;font-size:.75rem}
  .task-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .task-cb{width:15px;height:15px;border-radius:3px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);margin-top:1px;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .task-cb.done{background:var(--green-mid);border-color:var(--green-mid);color:#fff;font-size:10px}
  .task-text{flex:1;line-height:1.4}
  .task-text.done{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--muted)}
  .task-pri{font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:20px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
  /* GAUGE */
  .gauge-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;margin:6px 0}
  .gauge-val{font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:800;margin-top:-4px}
  .gauge-lbl{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--muted)}
  /* FORM */
  .form-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .form-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
  .form-label{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600}
  .form-input,.form-select{background:#1c3324;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;padding:8px 11px;color:var(--text);font-size:.8rem;outline:none;font-family:inherit}
  .form-input:focus,.form-select:focus{border-color:var(--green-mid)}
  .form-select option{background:#1c3324}
  /* WORKFLOW STEPS */
  .wf-step{display:flex;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1c3324;align-items:flex-start}
  .wf-step:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .wf-num{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
  .wf-done{background:#1a4d2e;color:var(--green-light);border:1.5px solid var(--green-mid)}
  .wf-active{background:#0d2a40;color:#93c5fd;border:1.5px solid #3b82f6}
  .wf-pending{background:#1c2e24;color:var(--muted);border:1.5px solid var(--border)}
  .wf-content .wf-title{font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:2px}
  .wf-content .wf-desc{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.4}
  .wf-content .wf-time{font-size:.67rem;color:var(--green-light);margin-top:3px}
  /* RISK TABLE */
  .risk-bar{height:6px;border-radius:3px;background:#1c3324;overflow:hidden;margin-top:3px}
  .risk-fill-low{background:var(--green-light);width:22%}
  .risk-fill-med{background:var(--yellow);width:55%}
  .risk-fill-high{background:var(--red);width:82%}
  /* CHARTS — CSS bars */
  .bar-chart{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:6px;height:80px;margin:8px 0}
  .bar-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex:1}
  .bar-rect{width:100%;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;min-height:4px;background:var(--green-mid);opacity:.8}
  .bar-label{font-size:.6rem;color:var(--muted);text-align:center}
  .bar-val{font-size:.62rem;color:var(--green-light)}
  /* GUARDRAIL BANNER */
  .guardrail-banner{background:#2a1505;border:1px solid #5a3010;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;font-size:.75rem}
  .guardrail-banner .gb-ico{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0}
  .guardrail-banner strong{color:var(--orange)}
  /* TOOLTIPS */
  [data-tip]{position:relative}
  [data-tip]:hover::after{content:attr(data-tip);position:absolute;bottom:110%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:#0d1f15;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:5px;padding:5px 9px;font-size:.67rem;color:var(--text);white-space:nowrap;z-index:99;pointer-events:none}
  /* SCROLL */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:6px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);border-radius:3px}
  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media(max-width:1100px){.layout{grid-template-columns:220px 1fr}.right-panel{display:none}.stats-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
  @media(max-width:700px){.layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}.sidebar{display:none}.stats-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-icon">🌾</div>
    <div class="logo-text">
      <h1>AgroMind AI Agent</h1>
      <p>Crop Management · Sustainability · Regulatory Compliance</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-badges">
    <span class="badge badge-green">✓ USDA Compliant</span>
    <span class="badge badge-green">✓ EPA Guardrails Active</span>
    <span class="badge badge-yellow">⚠ 2 Alerts</span>
    <span class="badge badge-blue">Season: Spring 2026</span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- LAYOUT -->
<div class="layout">

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<nav class="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-section">Operations</div>
  <div class="nav-item active" onclick="switchPanel('dashboard')"><span class="icon">📊</span> Dashboard</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('crops')"><span class="icon">🌱</span> Crop Planner</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('irrigation')"><span class="icon">💧</span> Irrigation AI</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('pest')"><span class="icon">🐛</span> Pest & Disease <span class="alert-dot"></span></div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('harvest')"><span class="icon">🌾</span> Harvest Scheduler</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('soil')"><span class="icon">🪨</span> Soil Analytics</div>
  <div class="sidebar-section">Intelligence</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('chat')"><span class="icon">🤖</span> AI Assistant</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('workflows')"><span class="icon">⚙️</span> Workflows</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('risk')"><span class="icon">⚡</span> Risk Engine <span class="alert-dot"></span></div>
  <div class="sidebar-section">Compliance</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('compliance')"><span class="icon">🛡️</span> Guardrails & Policy</div>
  <div class="nav-item" onclick="switchPanel('reports')"><span class="icon">📋</span> Audit Reports</div>
</nav>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<main class="main">

  <!-- DASHBOARD PANEL -->
  <div class="panel active" id="panel-dashboard">
    <div class="panel-top">
      <div><h2>📊 Farm Operations Dashboard</h2><p>Real-time overview — Willow Creek Farm, 480 acres</p></div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-ghost">↻ Sync Sensors</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary">+ New Task</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">

      <!-- STAT CARDS -->
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Active Crops</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:#6fcf97">7</div><div class="stat-sub">Across 6 fields · 480 ac</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Soil Moisture Avg</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:#3b82f6">64%</div><div class="stat-sub stat-trend up">↑ +3% vs yesterday</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Pending Actions</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:#f5c542">5</div><div class="stat-sub stat-trend warn">2 High Priority</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Yield Forecast</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:#6fcf97">+12%</div><div class="stat-sub stat-trend up">Above 5-yr avg</div></div>
      </div>

      <!-- ALERTS -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-head"><h3>🔔 Active Alerts & Edge Cases</h3><span class="pill pill-yellow">5 Open</span></div>
        <div class="section-body">
          <div class="alert-card alert-high">
            <div class="ico">🚨</div>
            <div>
              <div class="ac-title">HIGH — Late Blight Detected: Field 3 (Tomatoes)</div>
              <div class="ac-body">AI model confidence: 94% · Affected area: ~18 acres · Spread risk: HIGH within 48h<br>Regulatory note: Mancozeb application restricted — EPA buffer zone active within 200ft of creek.</div>
              <button class="ac-action" style="background:#5a2020;color:#f08080" onclick="switchPanel('pest')">→ Open Pest Module</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="alert-card alert-med">
            <div class="ico">⚠️</div>
            <div>
              <div class="ac-title">MEDIUM — Irrigation Anomaly: Field 6 (Corn)</div>
              <div class="ac-body">Sensor F6-N reports 29% below optimal soil VWC. Auto-schedule triggered but awaiting approval due to water-use permit threshold (87% used this month).</div>
              <button class="ac-action" style="background:#3d3010;color:#f5c542" onclick="switchPanel('irrigation')">→ Review Irrigation</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="alert-card alert-low">
            <div class="ico">✅</div>
            <div>
              <div class="ac-title">LOW — Harvest Window Opening: Field 1 (Winter Wheat)</div>
              <div class="ac-body">Optimal harvest window: Apr 2–7 · GDD accumulation on track · Weather model shows 91% dry-window probability. Auto-workflow queued.</div>
              <button class="ac-action" style="background:#1a3d28;color:#6fcf97" onclick="switchPanel('harvest')">→ Schedule Harvest</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="alert-card alert-info">
            <div class="ico">📋</div>
            <div>
              <div class="ac-title">INFO — Organic Certification Audit Due in 14 Days</div>
              <div class="ac-body">USDA NOP audit scheduled Apr 12. 3 documentation items pending. All pesticide logs and soil amendment records must be finalized.</div>
              <button class="ac-action" style="background:#112240;color:#93c5fd" onclick="switchPanel('compliance')">→ Compliance Panel</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CROP STATUS TABLE -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-head"><h3>🌱 Crop Status Overview</h3></div>
        <div class="section-body" style="padding:0">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Field</th><th>Crop</th><th>Growth Stage</th><th>Days to Harvest</th><th>Health Score</th><th>Status</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Field 1</td><td>Winter Wheat</td><td>Grain Fill</td><td>8</td><td><span style="color:#6fcf97;font-weight:700">92</span></td><td><span class="pill pill-green">Optimal</span></td><td><button class="btn btn-ghost" style="padding:4px 9px;font-size:.7rem" onclick="switchPanel('harvest')">Harvest Plan</button></td></tr>
              <tr><td>Field 2</td><td>Soybeans</td><td>V6 Vegetative</td><td>74</td><td><span style="color:#6fcf97;font-weight:700">87</span></td><td><span class="pill pill-green">Optimal</span></td><td><button class="btn btn-ghost" style="padding:4px 9px;font-size:.7rem">Monitor</button></td></tr>
